                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>The type of evidence supporting the recommendations is not specifically stated.</p>
<p>Table A-2 in the original guideline documents indicates the number and type of studies that addressed each of the key questions. The evidence base consists primarily of systematic reviews and randomized controlled trials.</p></div></p>

